---
const schedulingLink = 'https://calendly.com/aldogustavomalasomma/15min';
const briefHref =
  'mailto:hello@copycodeai.online?subject=' + encodeURIComponent('Fast Launch Request');
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-14 sm:px-8 lg:px-12" aria-labelledby="fast-launch-title">
  <h2 id="fast-launch-title" class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink-900">Fast Launch Engineering</h2>
  <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-slate-700">Launch first. Add automation where it helps. Fix structure before scale.</p>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Choose the work you need right now.</p>
  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Practical engineering work focused on structure, implementation, and delivery.</p>

  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Compliance-Ready Landing Page</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        A startup landing page or MVP site built to help you launch fast without creating avoidable GDPR or accessibility issues.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/compliance-ready-landing"
        class="mt-2 inline-flex text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        aria-label="Learn more about Compliance-Ready Landing Page"
      >
        Learn more
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">From €750</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Typical delivery: 3-5 days</p>
      <div class="mt-3 rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/70 p-3" data-offer-key="tallinn_landing_2026">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900" data-offer="price">Tallinn Launch Offer: EUR 650</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-emerald-800" data-offer="deadline">First 5 Tallinn startups · Ends 31 Mar 2026 (EET)</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-900" data-offer="slots" aria-live="polite">Slots left: 5</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600" data-offer="active">For Tallinn-based startups only.</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">AI Feature Integration</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Add useful automation when manual workflows start slowing your team down — without overengineering the product.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/ai-feature-integration"
        class="mt-2 inline-flex text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        aria-label="Learn more about AI Feature Integration"
      >
        Learn more
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">From €900</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Tactical implementation. Not enterprise AI.</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Typical delivery: 5-7 days</p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">EAA Structural Hardening</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Fix structural accessibility issues at code level so your product is easier to use, safer to scale, and closer to EAA/WCAG expectations.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/eaa-structural-hardening"
        class="mt-2 inline-flex text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
        aria-label="Learn more about EAA Structural Hardening"
      >
        Learn more
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">From €850</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Typical delivery: 2-4 days</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Need to launch, fix structure, or validate your setup?</h3>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
      Send a brief or book a short technical assessment. You’ll get clear next steps, and if the scope is a
      fit, I’ll reply with a fixed proposal.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
      <a
        href={schedulingLink}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-soft hover:bg-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
      >
        Start with a 15-min Technical Assessment
      </a>
      <a
        href={briefHref}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
      >
        Request a Brief Review
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">No sales pressure. Written follow-up included.</p>
  </div>
</section>
